    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在前作《Christmas Blaster》中，圣诞老人已经面对并击败了威胁圣诞节的邪恶生物克拉姆普斯。他的勇气和决心取得了胜利，恢复了和平与欢乐。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308050/extras/cd3ad2fa88faaf419ce51739f792f4d0.avif?t=1761946763\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在，在《Christmas Smash》中，克拉姆普斯卷土重来，煽动了一场精灵的大叛乱，并绑架了圣诞夫人，企图迫使圣诞老人放弃他的使命。圣诞老人以勇气和技能著称，他再次被召唤来面对迫在眉睫的危险，这次还要从克拉姆普斯和他那叛逆的精灵军队手中拯救他的挚爱。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308050/extras/5028d619340afcb49b6350a019255aaa.poster.avif?t=1761946763\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308050/extras/5028d619340afcb49b6350a019255aaa.webm?t=1761946763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308050/extras/5028d619340afcb49b6350a019255aaa.mp4?t=1761946763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中，圣诞老人将面对危险的挑战和强大的敌人，如腐败的精灵、机器和冰雪士兵。在盟友的帮助下，圣诞老人穿越雪地，最终到达克拉姆普斯的巢穴，与其展开一场史诗般的终极对决。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308050/extras/bbf0fdb889255c2a032e63b6216851cf.poster.avif?t=1761946763\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308050/extras/bbf0fdb889255c2a032e63b6216851cf.webm?t=1761946763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308050/extras/bbf0fdb889255c2a032e63b6216851cf.mp4?t=1761946763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接一场爆炸性且充满动作的冒险吧！</p>",
